---
import Handbook from "../layouts/Handbook.astro";
---
<Handbook title="Open Decisions" current="more">
  <h1>Open Decisions</h1>
  <section class="panel">
    <h2>D1 · 最終旅行日期</h2>
    <p>是否仍為 2027 年 3 月？確切起迄？</p>
    <span class="badge decision">DecisionRequired</span>
  </section>
  <section class="panel">
    <h2>D2 · 城市與停留天數</h2>
    <p>7 日／6 晚：是否採納 Provisional <strong>首爾 4N + 釜山 2N</strong>？或改 3N+3N／延長為 8 日以保留 4N+3N／單城？</p>
    <span class="badge decision">DecisionRequired</span>
  </section>
  <section class="panel">
    <h2>D3 · 航班機場</h2>
    <p>台灣出發機場與韓國進出機場偏好？</p>
    <span class="badge decision">DecisionRequired</span>
  </section>
</Handbook>
